md:
giải nghĩa từ "administrative" sang tiếng việt; đưa ra nghĩa tiếng việt theo từ loại và đưa ra câu ví dụ, các từ liên quan.

Administrative (adjective)

* Meaning: relating to the management of a business, organization, or country
* Vietnamese: hành chính
* Example sentence: The administrative staff are responsible for managing the day-to-day operations of the company.
* Related words: administration, administrator, administrate

Administrative (noun)

* Meaning: the management of a business, organization, or country
* Vietnamese: bộ phận hành chính
* Example sentence: The administrative department is in charge of handling all the paperwork and documentation.
* Related words: administration, administrator, administrate

Note: The word "administrative" can have different meanings depending on the context in which it is used. In general, it refers to the management or administration of a business, organization, or country.
